skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: batuu boarding pass
des:
Bright suns traveler! 
You are eager to explore Black Spire Outpost and its marvelous sights but first you need to arrive!. 
For this simple task, here's an Alexa Skill to keep you updated on which group is currently boarding to Batuu! 
Just open the skill to know the status of the boarding process or ask her to check for your group. 

NOTE: This is a non official skill for DLR Galaxy's Edge to check which groups can enter in the land. It's not affiliated to Disney or Lucasfilm and it's created only as a reference tool.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
